item.title: Help
item.dc:creator: @Cheesehunk Cheesehunk
item.description:
@Cheesehunk wrote:

Close all SCAR’s. Re-open them, and try again. If that doesn’t work, make sure you have no SCAR windows open, then re-download. After the download is complete you may open up SCAR again, and start autoing. SCAR doesn’t activate it’s Plugins at run-time.
